# Security headers are configured mostly in accordance with:
# - https://owasp.org/www-project-secure-headers/
# - https://cheatsheetseries.owasp.org/cheatsheets/HTTP_Headers_Cheat_Sheet.html
# - https://nextjs.org/docs/app/guides/content-security-policy#without-nonces
#
# They were tested with:
# - https://securityheaders.com/?q=<branch>-ravefree-website.spring-hat-8e4e.workers.dev&hide=on&followRedirects=on
#
# Caching headers are configured according to:
# - https://opennext.js.org/cloudflare/caching#static-assets-caching

