  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Cross-Origin-Resource-Policy: same-origin
  Permissions-Policy: accelerometer=(), autoplay=(), camera=(), clipboard-read=(), clipboard-write=(), cross-origin-isolated=(), display-capture=(), encrypted-media=(), fullscreen=(), gamepad=(), geolocation=(), gyroscope=(), hid=(), idle-detection=(), interest-cohort=(), keyboard-map=(), magnetometer=(), microphone=(), midi=(), payment=(), picture-in-picture=(), publickey-credentials-get=(), screen-wake-lock=(), serial=(), sync-xhr=(self), usb=(), web-share=(), xr-spatial-tracking=()
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
